   a clear understanding of the volatile nature of its internal dynamics,‚Äù
   says Soundararajan. ‚ÄúThere is not a single platform that has cultural
   competencies related to caste and religious extremism.‚Äù
   [tiny.gif] [img_0775.jpg]

