     *
   Google Stadia review: a terrible but tantalising glimpse of the future
       [tiny.gif] [googlestadia-1.jpg]

Google Stadia review: a terrible but tantalising glimpse of the future
         ______________________________________________________________

          +
          +
          +
          +
          +
          +
          +
          +
          +
          +
